org.la4j

Interface Vector

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Externalizable, Iterable<Double>, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractVector, BasicVector, CompressedVector, DenseVector, SparseVector

    public interface Vector
extends Externalizable, Iterable<Double>
    The real vector interface. A vector represents an array of elements. It can be re-sized.
